translate English day3_my_T_057d318d:


    nar "When all's said and done, that he spent all day running around looking for me means I'm clearly on his mind."


translate English day3_my_T_42146caa:


    nar "It's impossible to ignore that kind of goodwill, regardless of the reasoning behind it."


translate English day3_my_T_40dc54df:


    nar "And besides, I'm the only one who misses out by dwelling in this depressive state forever."


translate English day3_my_T_0ab97a85:


    nar "I have to get a grip and make sense of this mess. Closing my eyes, I lightly slap both of my cheeks."


translate English day3_my_T_80326f15:


    nar "Now then... having organized the department office, all that's left is tidying up the warehouse."


translate English day3_my_T_fbfe8dff:


    nar "In other words, Securett will most likely be locked up in that warehouse for the rest of the day, choking on dust."


translate English day3_my_T_437d8de5:


    nar "Meaning I won't have to see his lousy face until tomorrow--meaning a temporary break from his constant critiques!"


translate English day3_my_T_95b8f218:


    nar "When it comes to relaxing, there's nothing better than a breath of fresh air. It's much better than the musty warehouse or those moldy dorms."


translate English day3_my_T_3755dd06:


    nar "Maybe I'll even bump into someone who has the same affliction as me."


translate English day3_my_T_801f7fb6:


    nar "Priests still go about the temple in a hurry, their jobs still unfinished."


translate English day3_my_T_aa894645:


    nar "I let myself get swept away by the stream of people walking to and fro while trying not to get in their way. "


translate English day3_my_T_d74f27d7:


    nar "And before I know it, I'm heading down a familiar path toward the flower garden."


translate English day3_my_T_36eeeed5:


    nar "I catch a whiff of the refreshing scent of freshly watered flowers. This is one of only a few places around the temple where you can enjoy the fresh air. "


translate English day3_my_T_70693259:


    nar "And yet not too many folks stop by here. They're too busy to care about frivolous things like flowers and plants."


translate English day3_my_T_efa77c4d:


    nar "Coming out here to cool my head, I always feel like I'm escaping the temple's cramped confines."


translate English day3_my_T_6f7a0a06:


    nar "I brush past a rose that's hanging from the trellis, causing a small pool of rainwater that had built up within the petals to splash down on me."


translate English day3_my_T_0395cca4:


    nar "Though the rain that seemed to fall endlessly all morning has stopped, the sky remains just as gloomy."


translate English day3_my_T_8d9ca0c2:


    nar "With summer days ahead, it's only a matter of time before the sun reappears from behind the rain clouds, though if the rays are too strong, it'll cause the flowers to wither up and die."


translate English day3_my_T_38609bdd:


    nar "It's probably due to the everpresent polar night. "


translate English day3_my_T_4d22be50:


    nar "Still, Maya's beloved flowers will wither and die away if they don't get some sunlight soon."


translate English day3_my_T_36821dc8:


    nar "As I gaze off into the distance, thoughts idly swirling through my mind, I take in the entire garden."


translate English day3_my_T_7ff4cd03:


    nar "From within the familiar trees and familiar flowers, I spot a head of unfamiliar hair... It's Claire. And next to her is..."


translate English day3_my_T_72cd9e40:


    pl "Maya!"


translate English day3_my_T_d7965472:


    nar "I suddenly call out to her."


translate English day3_my_T_1d29dd34:


    nar "Hearing my voice, the two girls turn their attention toward me."


translate English day3_my_T_e18cdd66:


    cr "What are you doing over there, [na]!" with sshake


translate English day3_my_T_197dcbc1:


    pl "You took the words out of my mouth! I thought you'd already left for the day?" with sshake


translate English day3_my_T_28fd453a:


    nar "I know they heard me, but neither girl responds right away."


translate English day3_my_T_956f0c6d:


    nar "I can see them talking quietly to one another but they're too far away for me to hear anything."


translate English day3_my_T_58548e27:


    nar "As I half-heartedly wait for them to finish their private conversation,"


translate English day3_my_T_7762b4d9:


    nar "Claire, who appears so much smaller at a distance, waves me over."


translate English day3_my_T_8ee23250:


    nar "As I get closer, I realize they're sitting in white chairs, facing each other. "


translate English my_bbb82d09:


    pl "Oh... Wait, Maya! I'll head back with you!"


translate English my_9af8e870:


    my "...Whatever you want."


translate English my_b8e85901:


    nar "Without waiting for a response, she begins walking off, leaving the two of us still sitting there. My heart beats a little faster with each step Maya takes, gradually increasing the distance between us."


translate English my_65082009:


    cr "Well, I guess that's our signal to call it a night for now."


translate English my_4a1578a0:


    pl "Looks that way. I had a lot of fun today. I look forward to seeing you again."


translate English my_d3897756:


    cr "Likewise! I had a blast. Thanks so much! I'm sure I'll see you around."


translate English my_0d0453d8:


    nar "I'm glad we finally got to engage in a proper goodbye, although I'm worried about Maya heading off on her own. "


translate English my_5f03d323:


    nar "If I don't hurry, I won't be able to catch up..."


translate English my_ee898e3b:


    nar "As if noticing my impatience to be off, she climbs down from the chair, so much taller than herself, her smile never leaving her lips."


translate English my_aa824a11:


    cr "I'm heading toward the main entrance, which is in the opposite direction from you two."


translate English my_6dff78c8:


    pl "Oh, yeah? You seem to know your way around the temple better than I do."


translate English my_5b2b75dd:


    cr "That's right! And the reason why is none of your business~"


translate English my_1eb9edc4:


    pl "Well excuse me for snooping~"


translate English my_652d636d:


    nar "Contrary to my concern, Claire seems to be enjoying the situation, most likely because of her inclination toward gossiping."


translate English my_36f58293:


    nar "But I hope this doesn't lead to any weird misunderstandings..."


translate English my_20c746b7:


    cr "Keep working hard!"


translate English my_697227be:



    nvl clear
    nar "I hurry off, leaving our final goodbye behind us. Running as fast as I can, I'm quickly able to catch up to Maya."


translate English my_cae468c8:


    nar "She looks over at me, seemingly unsure of what to say. She's walking slower than usual, but she doesn't stop."


translate English my_2a23d460:


    nar "I walk beside her, matching my pace with hers."


translate English my_0807b8ad:


    my "...You're a good guy, [na2]."


translate English my_8702d58b:


    nar "Before I can say anything, Maya breaks the silence, staring at the ground in front of her."


translate English my_d427afce:


    nar "I honestly hadn't expected her to speak first, but it makes my full sprint to get here all worthwhile."


translate English my_44d1ea1b:


    my "You have the ability to get along with anyone. I'm...kind of jealous."


translate English my_3cb44643:


    pl "I'm happy you think that way, but it helped that I had such a nice person to talk to, like Claire."


translate English my_6dd56a5d:


    my "Yeah?"


translate English my_351bdd18:


    pl "I assumed she was just a spoiled, snobby rich girl. I never thought I'd be able to have such a great conversation with her. It's great we share a lot of the same hobbies..."


translate English my_857cf87a:


    pl "Haha! Wanna hear what she said after you left?"


translate English my_1239e5cf:


    my "...What did she say?"


translate English my_4c443a7d:


    pl "You see... Hrm... A-Actually, nevermind. The more I think about it, the weirder it seems to tell you... "


translate English my_d746792c:


    pl "N-Not that it's anything weird. I'll tell you later. Maybe we can go see that movie Claire mentioned together?"


translate English my_9fccedbe:


    my "You want to go with me? But I don't know anything about it."


translate English my_3b28b197:


    pl "I'll fill you in on anything you need to know! "


translate English my_a98b3abb:


    pl "I really think you'll enjoy it, though I know without a doubt that Securett jerk will have a problem with it."


translate English my_c5d203bd:


    pl "I wonder if I should invite him along... Haha! But as I said once myself, he can be a bit much."


translate English my_3334fc23:


    my "..."


translate English my_8e063f85:


    nar "As I fool around, laughing to myself, Maya suddenly stops. "


translate English my_74f520fe:


    nar "It was so unexpected that I had already taken a few steps before I realized she was no longer beside me."


translate English my_982ac364:


    nar "She's pretty quiet and very bad at expressing herself, but Maya also isn't one to ignore other people when they're talking to her. Which means she's clearly upset about something."


translate English my_e9a3eb5b:


    nar "I quietly return to where she's standing. The expression on her face is one I've never seen before."


translate English my_f02efb5a:


    nar "Her sullen, uninvitingly dark eyes turns on me, her cool gaze almost piercingly sharp."


translate English my_ad401e06:


    my "You're so insensitive, [na2]."


translate English my_522be39c:


    nar "Her words come through crystal clear, but I can't make heads or tails of them."


translate English my_5d505842:


    nar "With that said, she resumes walking, faster than before."


translate English my_bd9c6395:


    nar "I watch her small back get further and further away with each step, but I know I shouldn't chase after her this time."


translate English my_e9c3d7a2:


    nar "Left behind, all alone, I simply stand there, watching in bewilderment as she enters the dorms without incident."


translate English my_e2ead531:


    nar "Did I offend her in some way?"


translate English my_bdec154b:


    nar "Unsure what just happened, the more I think about her parting shot at me, the angrier I get."


translate English day3_meet_7bd82ca7:


    nar "Since Maya only ever seems to sit on one particular bench, "


translate English day3_meet_480c067c:


    nar "I didn't realize there were two chairs tucked away in the corner of the rose garden, with a small table between them."


translate English day3_meet_88407063:


    nar "What might have once been an outdoor terrace is now just an abandoned garden, overgrown with weeds and vines."


translate English day3_meet_5ddbcbfb:


    nar "It goes without saying there's no tea or cakes. The table is a simple affair, stained here and there with water spots from the rain."


translate English day3_meet_9275aa52:


    nar "And yet Claire's presence grants it an air of elegance."


translate English day3_meet_f70c97e9:


    nar "{nw}"


translate English day3_meet_fac58bac:


    cr "You're the last person I'd expect to see in a place like this! "


translate English day3_meet_ab406354:


    cr "What brings you here at this hour? Shouldn't you be working?"


translate English day3_meet_cf09461b:


    pl "It's lunchtime, so trainees like me are off the clock for now."


translate English day3_meet_ea6e7782:


    my "Oh, it's already that late?"


translate English day3_meet_04aa2c38:


    cr "My word! Is that so? I was having such a great chat that I lost track of the time!"


translate English day3_meet_f4a6deb2:


    cr "I'm not ready to say goodbye to my dear sweet Maya!"


translate English day3_meet_4f2dfd7b:


    nar "Dear sweet Maya...? I guess they did look pretty chummy when I saw them this morning."


translate English day3_meet_97a99dc3:


    pl "Do you two go way back or something?"


translate English day3_meet_3f85c755:


    my "N-Not at all! We're j-just... acquaintances... That's all."


translate English day3_meet_fd9e939b:


    nar "I can see Maya noticeably shrink, put off guard by my comment. As timid as always, she seems to be feeling out Claire's mood, not wanting to overstep any boundaries."


translate English day3_meet_f3012fa8:


    cr "I only met my dear sweet Maya today. Hmm... In fact, just this morning."


translate English day3_meet_867f77f8:


    cr "I arrived a little before most folks in the Cleanup Department arrive to start work. I had to help sort out supplies first, you see..."


translate English day3_meet_56c31b1b:


    pl "You came here that early? Then Maya must've had to get up before the sun did..."


translate English day3_meet_93c3e426:


    my "I-I'm used to it... I've always been an early riser."


translate English day3_meet_46c79738:


    pl "Ha! I used to get up that early back in my hometown."


translate English day3_meet_d001b2fb:


    cr "So then, you sleeping in late today was a one off?"


translate English day3_meet_4131bcbf:


    pl "Nope! I've never been a stickler for routines."


translate English day3_meet_61d3506b:


    cr "A person who doesn't follow the rules of the place they live in... Wow! You're such a free spirit!"


translate English day3_meet_48de193b:


    pl "Nah, I definitely got in trouble for that. But for a hard worker like you to come here so early in the morning?"


translate English day3_meet_8372bfb7:


    pl "And you're a guest, meaning you must've had a lot further to travel, right? What time did you wake up?"


translate English day3_meet_0dc238ea:


    cr "That's all true, though I actually came here even earlier than usual."


translate English day3_meet_5ed5ad7e:


    pl "You did? Why's that?"


translate English day3_meet_3cbf5fbf:


    cr "It should be obvious. I was excited to meet you! The marvelous, mysterious outsider!"


translate English day3_meet_eeabf80d:


    pl "M-Me...?"


translate English day3_meet_ff29df8d:


    cr "Of course! Hailing from far outside the capital, a small island in the far north that's said to be as hot as countries in the exotic east!"


translate English day3_meet_c562ef99:


    cr "Though little is known about it, various organizations and scholars visit regularly to confirm its history..."


translate English day3_meet_7fef4c86:


    cr "A land of dreams and adventures, overflowing with possibilities! Upon hearing that you came from such a place, I simply had to speak to you right away!"


translate English day3_meet_3f6c3d05:


    nar "I'm definitely not from this island she's talking about... Geez, who would even start such a rumor?"


translate English day3_meet_49566282:


    nar "I want to say something, but her eyes are sparkling somehow even more excitedly than this morning."


translate English day3_meet_bdc0c29c:


    nar "Is her overbearing attitude really nothing more than pure curiosity?"


translate English day3_meet_53e6189a:


    cr "Which... is why I want to apologize for how rude I was this morning. Again, I'm truly sorry."


translate English day3_meet_c488bb11:


    pl "Look, it's fine. I feel bad for shouting at you the way I did."


translate English day3_meet_f7667b83:


    nar "It's been weighing on my mind all day, so I'm glad I was able to apologize, no matter how short it might've been."


translate English day3_meet_280a4fab:


    nar "Claire giggles at my response. She's a whirlwind of emotions, switching from sullen to satisfied in a heartbeat."


translate English day3_meet_2be8a5d5:


    cr "At any rate! If you hadn't been so outstandingly late, we might have started off on the right foot this morning."


translate English day3_meet_89c8d902:


    pl "So that's how you ended up attached to Maya, who started the same day I did, yeah?"


translate English day3_meet_6e78cb94:


    cr "That's not entirely true. Although, to be fair, the reason why I chose Maya isn't that complicated."


translate English day3_meet_36234072:


    cr "Basically, she was the cutest person there!"


translate English day3_meet_b7da9b9f:


    my "What...?"


translate English day3_meet_91fb9d83:


    pl "Ah-ha! Yep, that makes perfect sense!"


translate English day3_meet_7d236369:


    my "S-Stop teasing me, you two...!"


translate English day3_meet_2799e120:


    cr "I'm not teasing you in the slightest! I thought you were adorable from the moment I laid eyes on you."


translate English day3_meet_d10a42bf:


    cr "With those soft, peach-colored curls, your belly as round as your head, wearing the type of ruffled skirt that's so in fashion right now in the capital..."


translate English day3_meet_91276a60:


    cr "Oh, and a slender build that makes you look younger than your age! Plus, those sad eyes of yours that make you look as adorable as a fragile baby animal!"


translate English day3_meet_a4fb2bee:


    pl "You're amazingly observant to see all that in a single glance."


translate English day3_meet_54dcb7c4:


    nar "Maya's face turns redder with each word, and she hangs her head, clearly very, very embarrassed."


translate English day3_meet_88354b8d:


    pl "No matter how much you flatter her, that spot next to her is reserved for me."


translate English day3_meet_8dc95d0f:


    cr "Ridiculous! My dear, dear sweet Maya, who do you like more?!"


translate English day3_meet_ea42d35a:


    my "...Please just knock it off already."


translate English day3_meet_827b6d03:


    cr "No way! This is a serious matter! Sweetest Maya, it's time for you to clock off work, correct?"


translate English day3_meet_a9f4300e:


    cr "Why don't we go see a movie together? Come on!"


translate English day3_meet_03de7972:


    cr "It's called \"Flowers in the Attic.\""


translate English day3_meet_f842965a:


    cr "It's a romantic horror film about the forbidden love affair between two siblings!"


translate English day3_meet_2fb93d9f:


    cr "And it's directed by a cinematic legend who's known for some of the best selling masterpieces in the capital! I'm sure you've heard about it, right?"


translate English day3_meet_8229f73b:


    my "Ngh..."


translate English day3_meet_ab4bd216:


    pl "Oh, right! I've heard of it. I didn't realize it came out already."


translate English day3_meet_822f1108:


    nar "I blurt the words out before I can stop myself. "


translate English day3_meet_6ac45287:


    nar "It's impossible to grow up without fascination about the capital, especially since it produces so much of all available entertainment that it almost seems like the center of the world itself."


translate English day3_meet_32b651c1:


    nar "Being in the middle of nowhere meant information was scant and hard to come by, though not impossible to collect."


translate English day3_meet_e2eb494b:


    nar "I learned what I could from soldiers on patrol and scholars passing through."


translate English day3_meet_21c84f99:


    nar "And so, enthralled by every scrap they threw my way, I grew up enthralled by that magical, distant place."


translate English day3_meet_d2cf6188:


    cr "You've seen other movies by that director before, [na]?"


translate English day3_meet_c09af1a4:


    pl "I grew up in a town so backwoods that we didn't even have radios, let alone a movie theater, so no, I haven't seen any. But I'm familiar with the plots..."


translate English day3_meet_20ef2047:


    pl "I read through the entire library of their works. That one's about the husband who falls in love with a girl while on a business trip, right?"


translate English day3_meet_5705571d:


    cr "\"Goose Season,\" right?! That one's truly a masterpiece!"


translate English day3_meet_be6e6447:


    cr "It ended up being delayed due to production issues, but the twist they threw in was wilder than anyone expected!"


translate English day3_meet_81edaaa0:


    pl "Right, right. That his affair partner thought his wife was just a friend the whole time! "


translate English day3_meet_73464f85:


    pl "A simple misunderstanding ending in tragedy... And with the delayed release, it felt like the film vanished from theaters overnight."


translate English day3_meet_3df333e6:


    cr "I know, right?! Though, to be fair, I'd been distracted by another movie that came out at the same time... "


translate English day3_meet_320eaad6:


    cr "Maybe you've heard of it?"


translate English day3_meet_eaa82dbb:


    pl "Indeed I have. Well, I read the plot. Though to be honest, I thought it was..."


translate English day3_meet_24c4486c:


    cr "Terrible!!!"


translate English day3_meet_04be8cb1:


    pl "Right! Exactly! You've got a pretty good sense for this kind of thing!!!"


translate English day3_meet_a2351ee7:


    cr "There's no way a work of that calibre should've been buried in obscurity by a popcorn thriller designed to sell tickets, but well... true genius is never understood in its own time!"


translate English day3_meet_ffd16fa2:


    nar "We give each other a merry high five. With her hand so much smaller than mine, the sound of our hands slapping together is less lighthearted than I expected."


translate English day3_meet_89b55be6:


    cr "I never thought I'd share a conversation like this with anyone! Please, don't just stand there, [na]! Have a seat! Make yourself cozy!"


translate English day3_meet_0ded685f:


    pl "It's a little late for that, isn't it? Also there's only two chairs."


translate English day3_meet_60fb716a:


    cr "In that case... I'll make room for you by sitting on my dear sweet Maya's lap! I believe the phrase, \"killing two birds with one stone\" fits this situation perfectly!"


translate English day3_meet_0088f2fc:


    pl "I believe \"slip of the tongue\" would work in this situation as well. Don't put poor Maya on the spot!"


translate English day3_meet_871d3eca:


    my "Should I leave...?"


translate English day3_meet_ef17172b:


    pl "No! I wouldn't have come all the way out here if it wasn't for you, Maya."


translate English day3_meet_43b46f2c:


    cr "That's right! I'd have no reason to stay here alone with this fine gentleman if you weren't here!"


translate English day3_meet_3334fc23:


    my "..."


translate English day3_meet_b23b1478:


    pl "Do you have a favorite movie, Maya?"


translate English day3_meet_04373950:


    my "Me? No... Sorry. I don't know much about them. I've never really had a chance to watch any."


translate English day3_meet_50e2d7e0:


    cr "Oh yeah? I guess there's not a lot of cinemas outside of the capital, huh? "


translate English day3_meet_849e8f0e:


    cr "I guess music is what most kids our age are into now a days!"


translate English day3_meet_c6e4c6c5:


    my "I do have a passing interest in it..."


translate English day3_meet_d63e22ff:


    cr "No matter who you ask, the singer representing the capital at the moment is Ms. Galactia!"


translate English day3_meet_c4d15e8a:


    cr "Her bold yet sensitive lyrics, written all by herself, speaks directly to the younger generation, captivating them! She's a famous musical actress as well!"


translate English day3_meet_69e0c436:


    my "Ngh..."


translate English day3_meet_7f060a15:


    pl "By musical, you mean the thing with the snake sandwich?"


translate English day3_meet_37614ea5:


    cr "I knew you'd know what I was talking about, [na]! And it was featured on the lunch menu as well!"


translate English day3_meet_9a2578e1:


    pl "It's better as a breakfast meal!"


translate English day3_meet_e4af25c4:


    my "...Wouldn't it taste exactly the same?"


translate English day3_meet_669bb0bf:


    nar "..."


translate English day3_meet_4fd0ea37:


    pl "Musicals are certainly not everyone's cup of tea. "


translate English day3_meet_a6a84d2a:


    pl "But I'm sure you'd fall in love with them if you saw a couple, Maya! Let me see if I can try to explain..."


translate English day3_meet_c1e027e7:


    cr "So the female protagonist starts off only liking ham sandwiches, and... Ugh! This is really frustrating! "


translate English day3_meet_8670f5df:


    cr "I feel like if I try explaining the whole thing to you, it'll lose everything that makes it hilarious. "


translate English day3_meet_a9799815:


    cr "You gotta see it for yourself! I'll take you to go see it whenever you have some free time, sweetest Maya!"


translate English day3_meet_eaad24f2:


    my "I don't really know much about musicals, but I have a feeling it's not something that has repeat performances..."


translate English day3_meet_92fe4170:


    my "I'm sorry for interrupting your fun conversation..."


translate English day3_meet_cd23eae2:


    cr "You don't need to apologize all the time! There must be something you like, right? Hmm..."


translate English day3_meet_669bb0bf_1:


    nar "......"


translate English day3_meet_288f5b75:


    nar "Our conversation devolves into silence. Claire's trying to think up a new topic of conversation and seems to be coming up blank."


translate English day3_meet_307ac8ee:


    nar "I can't think of anything Maya likes aside from flowers and animals, but the main point is, "


translate English day3_meet_1eb92b87:


    nar "how can we bring her out of her shell to break this silence as quickly as possible?"


translate English day3_meet_1e75ce1d:


    pl "Oh, hey. Wanna see something cool?"


translate English day3_meet_9c1114dc:


    my "Something cool?"


translate English day3_meet_11762044:


    pl "It's just a simple mind reading trick. Who should I try it on?"


translate English day3_meet_73d5d72c:


    cr "Oh, gosh! Me, me! Pick me! Pick me!"


translate English day3_meet_8654c1b9:


    pl "Do you have a piece of paper and a pen by chance?"


translate English day3_meet_ddd9a233:


    my "Of course we don't have anything of the--"


translate English day3_meet_90526e90:


    cr "Is a memo pad okay?"


translate English day3_meet_3334fc23_1:


    my "..."


translate English day3_meet_fdd079ff:


    pl "Great! Now Claire, I'm going to ask you three questions. I want you to think of the answer without saying out loud, and I'll write it down on this piece of paper."


translate English day3_meet_87fea370:


    cr "Hmm... My eyes are pretty sharp, [na], so you better not try writing all the answers down at the end!"


translate English day3_meet_8162e941:


    pl "Maya's job is to help make sure I don't cheat, so no need to worry. "


translate English day3_meet_f05487a5:


    pl "Okay... Think about what month you were born in."


translate English day3_meet_44449ebd:


    cr "This is how they trick naive girls into giving out personal information...!"


translate English day3_meet_e324116a:


    pl "You have a great taste in movies, but maybe you should consider cutting back on fiction a bit!"


translate English day3_meet_cb06c70f:


    cr "And if I did so, you'd be the one languishing in sorrow!"


translate English day3_meet_343ecf3a:


    pl "I'm truly honored you feel that way about me."


translate English day3_meet_a8162656:


    nar "Maya has a look of doubt on her face as she keeps an eye on the piece of paper. "


translate English day3_meet_51d45059:


